Package com.msasc.lib.db

Class FieldProperties

java.lang.Object
com.msasc.lib.db.FieldProperties
public class FieldProperties extends Object
Helper to get/set additional properties of the field, like header, label, uppercase, and any visual or layout properties.
Author:
Miquel Sas
